com.paypal.selion.grid

Class ProcessLauncherConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paypal.selion.grid.LauncherConfiguration
      • com.paypal.selion.grid.ProcessLauncherConfiguration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LauncherOptions, ProcessLauncherOptions

    public class ProcessLauncherConfiguration
extends LauncherConfiguration
implements ProcessLauncherOptions
    SeLion Grid process configuration options which are shared across all RunnableLaunchers which spawn a new process, usually a Java one.
